Name: UCSB
Description: An awesome university that gives you a balance of education and entertainment.

Name: Goleta Home Depot
Description: An awesome palce to spend some time and money on improving your DIY game. Cool forklift drivers too.

Name: Cold Springs Tavern
Description: Tucked away in the mountains looking over Santa Barbara, this place has some of the best views and tri-tip sandwiches SB has to offer. If you can snag a ride, I would definitely recommend stopping by.

Name: The Granada Theater
Description: From music concerts to entertaining stage plays, this place has it all. A must visit for any visitor or resident of SB

Name: Stearns Wharf
Description: The perfect weekend spot for tourists and locals. Beautiful views, great food, and quirky shops.

Name: Raising Cane's Chicken Fingers
Description: Some of the most fire chicken fingers you will ever eat. This is the closest one to UCSB, but believe me when I tell you that the 3 hour drive is WELL worth it. KFC ain't got nothing on Cane's
